text: Chakori is a Pakistani Urdu movie. This movie was released on March 23, 1967, on Eid-ul-Azha Day in Dacca, East Pakistan (now Bangladesh). The movie was directed by Captain Ehtisham. It was Nadeem Baig's and Shabana's debut movie. Category:1960s Pakistani movies Category:1967 movies Category:Urdu-language movies
title: Chakori (1967 movie)
